{"id":14982,"date":"2022-08-24T09:16:29","date_gmt":"2022-08-24T02:16:29","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/sonamedia.site\/?p=14982"},"modified":"2022-08-30T14:05:24","modified_gmt":"2022-08-30T07:05:24","slug":"ban-sao-cd","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/sonamedia.site\/ban-sao-cd.html\/","title":{"rendered":"Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u c\u1ea7n bi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 b\u1ea3n sao CD"},"content":{"rendered":"<div id=\"ez-toc-container\" class=\"ez-toc-v2_0_36 counter-hierarchy ez-toc-counter ez-toc-grey ez-toc-container-direction\">\n<div class=\"ez-toc-title-container\">\n<p class=\"ez-toc-title\">N\u1ed9i Dung<\/p>\n<span class=\"ez-toc-title-toggle\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"ez-toc-pull-right ez-toc-btn ez-toc-btn-xs ez-toc-btn-default ez-toc-toggle\" style=\"display: none;\"><label for=\"item\" aria-label=\"Table of Content\"><span style=\"display: flex;align-items: center;width: 35px;height: 30px;justify-content: center;\"><svg style=\"fill: #999;color:#999\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\" class=\"list-377408\" width=\"20px\" height=\"20px\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\"><path d=\"M6 6H4v2h2V6zm14 0H8v2h12V6zM4 11h2v2H4v-2zm16 0H8v2h12v-2zM4 16h2v2H4v-2zm16 0H8v2h12v-2z\" fill=\"currentColor\"><\/path><\/svg><svg style=\"fill: #999;color:#999\" class=\"arrow-unsorted-368013\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\" width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" version=\"1.2\" baseProfile=\"tiny\"><path d=\"M18.2 9.3l-6.2-6.3-6.2 6.3c-.2.2-.3.4-.3.7s.1.5.3.7c.2.2.4.3.7.3h11c.3 0 .5-.1.7-.3.2-.2.3-.5.3-.7s-.1-.5-.3-.7zM5.8 14.7l6.2 6.3 6.2-6.3c.2-.2.3-.5.3-.7s-.1-.5-.3-.7c-.2-.2-.4-.3-.7-.3h-11c-.3 0-.5.1-.7.3-.2.2-.3.5-.3.7s.1.5.3.7z\"\/><\/svg><\/span><\/label><input type=\"checkbox\" id=\"item\"><\/a><\/span><\/div>\n<nav><ul class='ez-toc-list ez-toc-list-level-1' ><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-1\" href=\"https:\/\/sonamedia.site\/ban-sao-cd.html\/#Ban_sao_CD_la_gi\" title=\"B\u1ea3n sao CD l\u00e0 g\u00ec?\">B\u1ea3n sao CD l\u00e0 g\u00ec?<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-2\" href=\"https:\/\/sonamedia.site\/ban-sao-cd.html\/#Tieu_chuan\" title=\"Ti\u00eau chu\u1ea9n\">Ti\u00eau chu\u1ea9n<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-3\" href=\"https:\/\/sonamedia.site\/ban-sao-cd.html\/#Luu_y_trong_sao_chep_CD\" title=\"L\u01b0u \u00fd trong sao ch\u00e9p CD\">L\u01b0u \u00fd trong sao ch\u00e9p CD<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-4\" href=\"https:\/\/sonamedia.site\/ban-sao-cd.html\/#Exact_Audio_Copy\" title=\"Exact Audio Copy\">Exact Audio Copy<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/nav><\/div>\n<p>\u0110\u0129a CD l\u00e0 t\u00ean g\u1ecdi \u0111\u00e3 qu\u00e1 quen thu\u1ed9c v\u1edbi ch\u00fang ta. Nh\u01b0ng c\u00f2n nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ecbnh ngh\u0129a kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 CD th\u00ec ch\u01b0a ch\u1eafc ai c\u0169ng n\u1eafm r\u00f5. H\u00e3y c\u00f9ng \u00c1 Ch\u00e2u Media hi\u1ec3u r\u00f5 v\u1ec1 kh\u00e1i ni\u1ec7m n\u00e0y.<\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Ban_sao_CD_la_gi\"><\/span>B\u1ea3n sao CD l\u00e0 g\u00ec?<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>\u0110\u0129a\u00a0compact\u00a0ho\u1eb7c b\u1ea3n sao <a href=\"https:\/\/sonamedia.site\/dvd-cd-su-khac-biet-la-gi-dvd-cd-su-khac-biet-la-gi.html\/\">CD<\/a> l\u00e0 b\u1ea3n sao ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c c\u1ee7a d\u1eef li\u1ec7u g\u1ed1c ho\u1eb7c \u0111\u0129a CD nh\u1ea1c. C\u00f3 v\u00f4 s\u1ed1 ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh ph\u1ea7n m\u1ec1m c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o ra m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3n sao \u0111\u0129a CD. C\u00e1c b\u1ea3n sao d\u1ef1 ph\u00f2ng ho\u1eb7c c\u00e1c b\u1ea3n sao b\u1ed5 sung c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t \u0111\u0129a CD cho m\u1ee5c \u0111\u00edch c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n.<\/p>\n<p>Trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u0129a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n, m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u1ecf h\u01a1n c\u00e1c ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh\u00a0sao ch\u00e9p\u00a0s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i c\u00e1c ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh <a href=\"https:\/\/vi.wikipedia.org\/wiki\/Qu%E1%BA%A3n_l%C3%BD_b%E1%BA%A3n_quy%E1%BB%81n_k%E1%BB%B9_thu%E1%BA%ADt_s%E1%BB%91#:~:text=C%C3%A1c%20c%C3%B4ng%20c%E1%BB%A5%20Qu%E1%BA%A3n%20l%C3%BD,t%C3%A1c%20ph%E1%BA%A9m%20c%C3%B3%20b%E1%BA%A3n%20quy%E1%BB%81n.\">Qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd Quy\u1ec1n K\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt s\u1ed1 (DRM)<\/a> gi\u1ea3 m\u1ea1o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u0103n ch\u1eb7n vi\u1ec7c sao ch\u00e9p.<\/p>\n<p>C\u00e1c k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch ng\u0103n ch\u1eb7n sao ch\u00e9p nh\u1eb1m ng\u0103n ch\u1eb7n vi ph\u1ea1m b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n, m\u1eb7c d\u00f9 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ng\u01b0\u1eddi tin r\u1eb1ng theo h\u1ecdc thuy\u1ebft s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng h\u1ee3p ph\u00e1p l\u00e0 quy\u1ec1n c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ec3 sao ch\u00e9p c\u00e1c t\u00e0i li\u1ec7u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c mua h\u1ee3p ph\u00e1p ho\u1eb7c c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ee3p ph\u00e1p \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng cho ri\u00eang h\u1ecd.<\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_15028\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-15028\" style=\"width: 1000px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-15028 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/sonamedia.site\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/CD.jpg\" alt=\"Ban-sao-cd\" width=\"1000\" height=\"603\" srcset=\"https:\/\/sonamedia.site\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/CD.jpg 1000w, https:\/\/sonamedia.site\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/CD-300x181.jpg 300w, https:\/\/sonamedia.site\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/CD-768x463.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-15028\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">B\u1ea3n sao CD<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Tieu_chuan\"><\/span>Ti\u00eau chu\u1ea9n<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>M\u1ed9t ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh sao ch\u00e9p \u0111\u0129a CD t\u1ed1t ph\u1ea3i ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u1edbi b\u1ed1n\u00a0\u0111\u1ecbnh d\u1ea1ng\u00a0\u0111\u0129a quang c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n ho\u1eb7c ti\u00eau chu\u1ea9n.<\/p>\n<p>Ch\u00fang bao g\u1ed3m c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh d\u1ea1ng ghi m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a:<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>CD-R<\/li>\n<li>CD + R<\/li>\n<li>CD-RW<\/li>\n<li>CD + RW<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ghi l\u1ea1i. M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eadn ra c\u00e1c ti\u00eau chu\u1ea9n \u00edt \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng h\u01a1n nh\u01b0:<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>Super Audio CD (SACD)<\/li>\n<li>Video CD ( VCD ).<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>Ki\u1ec3m tra th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt c\u1ee7a ph\u1ea7n m\u1ec1m \u0111\u1ec3 bi\u1ebft t\u00ednh t\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u00edch tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 th\u1eddi gian ho\u1eb7c ti\u1ec1n b\u1ea1c v\u00e0o ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh sao ch\u00e9p. Ph\u1ea7n m\u1ec1m ghi \u0111\u0129a \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c y\u00eau c\u1ea7u \u0111\u1ec3 sao ch\u00e9p \u0111\u0129a karaoke , s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ecbnh d\u1ea1ng k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3 h\u1ecda cho l\u1eddi b\u00e0i h\u00e1t v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3n \u00e2m thanh, \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1ecdi l\u00e0 CD + G.<\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_15027\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-15027\" style=\"width: 1000px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-15027 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/sonamedia.site\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/burning-cd.jpg\" alt=\"Phan-mem-dia-CD\" width=\"1000\" height=\"719\" srcset=\"https:\/\/sonamedia.site\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/burning-cd.jpg 1000w, https:\/\/sonamedia.site\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/burning-cd-300x216.jpg 300w, https:\/\/sonamedia.site\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/burning-cd-768x552.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-15027\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Ph\u1ea7n m\u1ec1m ghi \u0111\u0129a CD c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3n sao c\u1ee7a \u0111\u0129a CD.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Luu_y_trong_sao_chep_CD\"><\/span>L\u01b0u \u00fd trong sao ch\u00e9p CD<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng thu\u1eadt ng\u1eef \u201cCD\u201d m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch bao h\u00e0m \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ec9 b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 lo\u1ea1i \u0111\u0129a quang n\u00e0o k\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 DVD.<\/li>\n<li>DVD kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi phim m\u00e0 l\u00e0 \u0111\u0129a media tr\u1ed1ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u01b0u tr\u1eef nhi\u1ec1u \u00e2m thanh v\u00e0 d\u1eef li\u1ec7u h\u01a1n so v\u1edbi CD.<\/li>\n<li>Kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh sao ch\u00e9p \u0111\u0129a CD \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng sao ch\u00e9p \u0111\u0129a DVD.<\/li>\n<li>N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n sao ch\u00e9p DVD hai l\u1edbp, h\u00e3y \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o r\u1eb1ng ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y. C\u00e1c ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh d\u00e0nh ri\u00eang cho sao ch\u00e9p DVD c\u0169ng c\u00f3 s\u1eb5n, nh\u01b0ng ch\u1ec9 m\u1ed9t t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 nh\u1ecf trong s\u1ed1 n\u00e0y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ec3 sao ch\u00e9p \u0111\u0129a DVD \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 b\u1eb1ng DRM, nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 n\u00eau tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00e2y.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<figure id=\"attachment_15030\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-15030\" style=\"width: 997px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-15030 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/sonamedia.site\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/students.jpg\" alt=\"Tao-ban-sao-trai-phep-se-vi-pham-ban-quyen\" width=\"997\" height=\"800\" srcset=\"https:\/\/sonamedia.site\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/students.jpg 997w, https:\/\/sonamedia.site\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/students-300x241.jpg 300w, https:\/\/sonamedia.site\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/students-768x616.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 997px) 100vw, 997px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-15030\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">T\u1ea1o b\u1ea3n sao tr\u00e1i ph\u00e9p c\u1ee7a \u00e2m nh\u1ea1c cho b\u1ea1n b\u00e8 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t h\u00ecnh th\u1ee9c vi ph\u1ea1m b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Ph\u1ea7n m\u1ec1m\u00a0sao ch\u00e9p t\u1ea1o b\u1ea3n sao \u0111\u0129a CD b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch sao ch\u00e9p \u0111\u0129a g\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean v\u00e0o\u00a0\u1ed5 c\u1ee9ng\u00a0d\u01b0\u1edbi d\u1ea1ng \u1ea3nh \u0111\u0129a.\u00a0Sau khi ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t, ph\u1ea7n m\u1ec1m s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ea9y khay CD ra v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1eeda s\u1ed5 b\u1eadt l\u00ean y\u00eau c\u1ea7u ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng \u0111\u01b0a \u0111\u0129a tr\u1eafng v\u00e0o.\u00a0Sau \u0111\u00f3, ph\u1ea7n m\u1ec1m ghi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh v\u00e0o \u0111\u0129a m\u1edbi, t\u1ea1o m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3n sao ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o.<\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Exact_Audio_Copy\"><\/span>Exact Audio Copy<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>M\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh\u00a0ph\u1ea7n m\u1ec1m mi\u1ec5n ph\u00ed\u00a0ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn v\u00e0 l\u00e2u \u0111\u1eddi nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 sao ch\u00e9p \u0111\u0129a CD \u00e2m thanh l\u00e0\u00a0<em>Exact Audio Copy (EAC)<\/em>. Wiethoff vi\u1ebft EAC v\u00e0o n\u0103m 1998. EAC chuy\u1ec3n c\u00e1c b\u1ea3n nh\u1ea1c t\u1eeb \u0111\u0129a CD \u00e2m thanh ti\u00eau chu\u1ea9n sang \u0111\u1ecbnh d\u1ea1ng s\u00f3ng (wav), sau \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh d\u1ea1ng di \u0111\u1ed9ng h\u01a1n (n\u00e9n) kh\u00e1c nh\u01b0 MP3. Ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ca ng\u1ee3i v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng sao ch\u00e9p c\u00e1c \u0111\u0129a CD b\u1ecb l\u1ea1m d\u1ee5ng, m\u00f2n ho\u1eb7c h\u01b0 h\u1ecfng, tuy nhi\u00ean, c\u00e1c t\u00ednh n\u0103ng v\u00e0 giao di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a n\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 qu\u00e1 cao c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1edbi.<\/p>\n<p>Nhi\u1ec1u ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh m\u1edbi h\u01a1n c\u00f3 giao di\u1ec7n \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n h\u01a1n v\u00e0 \u00edt t\u00f9y ch\u1ecdn k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt h\u01a1n cho ph\u00e9p ngay c\u1ea3 m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1edbi b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1ea1o b\u1ea3n sao \u0111\u0129a CD ch\u1ec9 v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t ho\u1eb7c hai l\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5p chu\u1ed9t.\u00a0<em>ImgBurn<\/em> l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh ph\u1ea7n m\u1ec1m mi\u1ec5n ph\u00ed. N\u00f3 cung c\u1ea5p:<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>Nh\u1eefng g\u00ec t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t, giao di\u1ec7n g\u1ecdn g\u00e0ng<\/li>\n<li>C\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c sao ch\u00e9p nhanh ch\u00f3ng v\u00e0 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng<\/li>\n<li>Cung c\u1ea5p c\u00e1c t\u00ednh n\u0103ng n\u00e2ng cao cho nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi mu\u1ed1n ch\u00fang.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh sao ch\u00e9p kh\u00e1c bao g\u1ed3m:<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li><em>CDBurnerXP<\/em><\/li>\n<li><em>InfraRecorder<\/em><\/li>\n<li><em>DeepBurner<\/em><\/li>\n<li><em>Ultimate CD \/ DVD Burner<\/em><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh kh\u00e1c. Ki\u1ec3m tra th\u01b0 vi\u1ec7n ph\u1ea7n m\u1ec1m y\u00eau th\u00edch c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u00eam s\u1ef1 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn v\u00e0 nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng.<\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_15029\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-15029\" style=\"width: 851px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\